    <a href="/" class="btn btn-gold mt-3">‚Üê Back to Home</a>
    <p class="note">Need help or changes to your order? <br>Reach us at <a href="mailto:craftwithastha@gmail.com" style="color: var(--gold); text-decoration: none;">craftwithastha@gmail.com</a></p>
  </div>

</body>
</html>
